        "content": "<p>Why is the rewrite tactic failing in line 126?<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/aDtdjLvHQVEeblPe8PUXITCi/Screenshot-2025-04-28-at-7.48.39AM.png\">Screenshot 2025-04-28 at 7.48.39 AM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/aDtdjLvHQVEeblPe8PUXITCi/Screenshot-2025-04-28-at-7.48.39AM.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-04-28 at 7.48.39 AM.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"2899x933\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/aDtdjLvHQVEeblPe8PUXITCi/Screenshot-2025-04-28-at-7.48.39AM.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
        "id": 514757393,
